{
  "stem": "12494.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Yeah, there were-- there were some terrible things that happened.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "In Hungary, there was, in 1941, the Jews who were not Hungarian citizens were gathered together, were expelled, and put into Kamianets-Podilskyi, which was Ukraine, Poland, depending on which year you looked at it, and were killed there.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the rumor of that became known.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "When the Yugoslavian crisis broke out in April, 1941, when the attack of the Germans on Yugoslavia occurred, with the help of the Hungarians-- the Hungarian government participated in that.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It's actually a complicated story.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The Hungarian prime minister committed suicide because he didn't want to participate.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The next prime minister, [INAUDIBLE], she did participate.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "There were atrocities committed by the Hungarian troops against the Jews in [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And several hundred Jews were killed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We heard about that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But in Hungary proper, there was no killing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "In Hungary proper, there was a systematic [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] anti-Jewish legislation which deprived much of the Jewish population of their livelihood.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It didn't really affect my father.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father was heading a variety of major corporations, and, as it happens very frequently, the rich people became richer, and the poor people became poorer.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I heard about these things.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I remember a conversation I had about the deportation in-- the deportation of the non-Hungarian citizen Jews with my father.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my father, of course, was himself quite concerned, because his family was naturalized Hungarian citizens.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But after that-- after a while, that went away.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I recall a conversation I had with one of my so-called classmates.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We-- there were a few of us who didn't go to school but who weren't public students but were private students.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we met at a given day in the year to pass our examinations together.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
